name: Open_Infos_Table
description: Informa√ßoes de Aberturas dos ultimos 7 dias, a partir da data do sistema
queryText:
SELECT o.SubscriberKey,
o.SubscriberID,
o.JobID,
o.EventDate,
IIF(o.IsUnique='True',1,0) AS IsUnique
FROM [_Open] o
WHERE
month(EventDate) = month(getdate()-1) 
and 
year(EventDate) = year(getdate()-1)
